or>Om</dc:creator><category>玄关</category><category>丹道</category><category>道</category></item><item><title>道教神咒</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%92/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%92/</guid><description>净心神咒 太上台星，应变无停。 驱邪缚魅，保命护身。 智慧明净，心神安宁。 三魂永久，魄无丧倾。 急急如律令。 净口神咒 丹朱口神，吐秽除氛。舌神正伦，通</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道</category><category>咒</category></item><item><title>洞玄灵宝定观经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>诵读 天尊告左玄真人曰：夫欲修道，先能舍事。 外事都绝，无与忤心。然后安坐，内观心起。若觉一念起，须除灭, 务令安静。 其次，虽非的有贪着，浮游乱想</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>高上玉皇心印妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上药三品，神与气精，恍恍惚惚，杳杳冥冥. 存无守有，顷刻而成，回风混合，百日功灵。 默朝上帝，一纪飞升，智者易悟，昧者难行。 履践天光，呼吸育清，</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄帝阴符经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上篇 观天之道，执天之行，尽矣。故天有五贼，见之者昌。五贼在心，施行于天。宇宙在乎手，万化生乎身。天性，人也；人心，机也。立天之道，以定人也。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>阴符经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭内景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%86%85%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%86%85%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上清章第一 上清紫霞虚皇前，太上大道玉晨君。闲居蕊珠作七言，散化五形变万神。 是为黄庭曰内篇，琴心三叠舞胎仙。九气映明出霄间，神盖童子生紫烟。 是</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭外景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%96%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E5%A4%96%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上部经第一 老君闲居作七言，解说身形及诸神。上有黄庭下关元，后有幽阙前命门。 呼吸庐间入丹田，玉池清水灌灵根。审能修之可长存，黄庭中人衣朱衣。 关</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄庭中景经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>念吾头顶戴天神 发为星辰万余纶 纡长槃屈光若玄 顶上中央名通天 孔德之容大如钱 天星和气从此间 养人骨髓浸灵根 下和六府绍五宫 消除恶气出脐门 还念两目白黑分</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>黄庭经</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>金花的秘密</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%